{"id":4593,"date":"2019-12-05T16:59:19","date_gmt":"2019-12-06T00:59:19","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/sfifoundation.com\/?p=4593"},"modified":"2019-12-05T16:59:21","modified_gmt":"2019-12-06T00:59:21","slug":"jennifer-faye-named-president-of-sfi","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/sfifoundation.com\/jennifer-faye-named-president-of-sfi\/","title":{"rendered":"Jennifer Faye Named President of SFI"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"404\" height=\"170\" src=\"http:\/\/sfifoundation.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/SFI-Logo.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-4428\" srcset=\"https:\/\/sfifoundation.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/SFI-Logo.png 404w, https:\/\/sfifoundation.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/SFI-Logo-300x126.png 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 404px) 100vw, 404px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>In\nrecently held elections, the SFI Board of Directors named Jennifer Faye as\nPresident of the Foundation. Jennifer has over 24 years of experience at SFI,\nher last 6 years serving as Vice President. Jennifer will continue to oversee\nthe business operations, administration, laboratory testing, and technical\ndepartments of SFI. Past President Arnie Kuhns remains with the company and on\nthe Board as Chief Executive Officer.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>\u201cSFI has a long history of serving the motorsports community for the betterment of safety and I\u2019m excited to be in a position to lead the next generation of SFI while honoring past traditions,\u201d said Jennifer. \u201cArnie has been a great mentor and role model, and I am honored to continue the important work that SFI does for the racing industry. We have a talented team of people at SFI, with each one of them contributing to our success in fulfilling our mission. I\u2019m proud to be a part of that team.\u201d<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Arnie added, &#8220;It is with a great deal of pride that we announce Jennifer Faye as the new President of SFI.\u00a0She has a great deal of experience with us and has proven to have\u00a0intelligence, dedication, and knowledge to take SFI to the next level. We know the industry will benefit from her efforts.&#8221;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>The SFI Foundation, Inc. (SFI) is a non-profit organization established to issue and administer standards for the quality assurance of specialty performance and racing parts and equipment. SFI also provides technical inspector certification and incident response training services to its member sanctioning bodies. SFI\u2019s programs are utilized worldwide in all racing disciplines. The SFI Foundation has served the automotive aftermarket and the motorsports industry since 1978. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>In recently held elections, the SFI Board of Directors named Jennifer Faye as President of the Foundation. Jennifer has over 24 years of experience at SFI, her last 6 years serving as Vice President. Jennifer will continue to oversee the business operations, administration, laboratory testing, and technical<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":3,"featured_media":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[43,7],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-4593","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","hentry","category-articles","category-general"],"aioseo_notices":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/sfifoundation.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4593","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/sfifoundation.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/sfifoundation.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/sfifoundation.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/sfifoundation.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=4593"}],"version-history":[{"count":2,"href":"https:\/\/sfifoundation.com\